    <title type="html"><![CDATA[SublimeText2で日本語入力をTabで。]]></title>
    <link href="http://makotow.github.com/blog/2013/05/05/sublimetext-japanese-input/"/>
    <updated>2013-05-05T17:50:00+09:00</updated>
    <id>http://makotow.github.com/blog/2013/05/05/sublimetext-japanese-input</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>概要</h2>

<p>ちょっと不便だなと思いつつ放置して使ってたけど、
少し調べたらわかったのでメモ。</p>

<ul>
<li>Google日本語入力を使用中</li>
<li>SublimeText2上で日本語入力中に入力候補が表示される→Tabで候補を選ぼうとする。</li>
<li>SublimeText2に制御が移るため、日本語消える。</li>
</ul>


<h2>対策方法</h2>

<ul>
<li>SublimeText2での制御を外す。</li>
<li>解決したかが外したことによる影響はまだ出ていないので様子見</li>
</ul>


<p>Sublime Text2 > Preferences > Key Bindings - Default を選択して、以下の部分をコメントアウト。
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='json'><span class='line'><span class="err">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;//</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="nt">&quot;keys&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">&quot;tab&quot;</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="nt">&quot;command&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&quot;insert_best_completion&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nt">&quot;args&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="nt">&quot;default&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&quot;\t&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nt">&quot;exact&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="kc">true</span><span class="p">}</span> <span class="p">}</span><span class="err">,</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">//</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="nt">&quot;keys&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">&quot;tab&quot;</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="nt">&quot;command&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&quot;insert_best_completion&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nt">&quot;args&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="nt">&quot;default&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&quot;\t&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nt">&quot;exact&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="kc">false</span><span class="p">},</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">//</span>  <span class="nt">&quot;context&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">//</span>  <span class="p">[</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">//</span>      <span class="p">{</span> <span class="nt">&quot;key&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&quot;setting.tab_completion&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nt">&quot;operator&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&quot;equal&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nt">&quot;operand&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="kc">true</span> <span class="p">}</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">//</span>  <span class="p">]</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">//</span> <span class="p">}</span><span class="err">,</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="err">&lt;p&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>以下のURLを参考にさせていただいた。</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.sanographix.net/2013/02/sublime-text-2/">Sublime Text 2 の設定したメモ</a></li>
</ul>

]]></content>
