  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[shでコマンドが存在するか確認する方法]]></title>
    <link href="http://makotow.github.com/blog/2013/03/31/sh-tech-exists-command/"/>
    <updated>2013-03-31T00:41:00+09:00</updated>
    <id>http://makotow.github.com/blog/2013/03/31/sh-tech-exists-command</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>zshの起動スクリプトないでうっかりMac固有の設定を入れてしまっていたので、
Linuxで起動した時にエラーが出てしまったのでコマンドがあるかで対応した。</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='sh'><span class='line'><span class="k">if </span>which brew &gt; /dev/null;then
</span><span class='line'>   . &lt;code&gt;brew --prefix&lt;/code&gt;/etc/profile.d/z.sh
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">fi</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>こんな方法もあるみたい</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='sh'><span class='line'><span class="k">if</span> <span class="o">[</span> -x <span class="s2">&quot;&lt;code&gt;which brew&lt;/code&gt;&quot;</span> <span class="o">]</span>;<span class="k">then</span>
</span><span class='line'>   . &lt;code&gt;brew --prefix&lt;/code&gt;/etc/profile.d/z.sh
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">fi</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>
]]></content>
